## Project Overview
{{.Description}}

## Tech Stack
- **Language**: PHP 8.3
- **Framework**: Laravel 11
- **Database**: PostgreSQL 17 (via Docker)
- **ORM**: Eloquent
- **Web Server**: Nginx + PHP-FPM (Docker)

## Project Structure
- `app/Http/Controllers/` - HTTP controllers
- `app/Models/` - Eloquent model classes
- `app/Providers/` - Service providers
- `config/` - Configuration files
- `database/migrations/` - Database migration files
- `routes/web.php` - Web routes
- `routes/api.php` - API routes
- `resources/views/` - Blade templates
- `tests/` - Test suite (Feature and Unit)
- `docs/supporting/` - Supporting documentation

## Development Commands
```bash
make start      # Start Docker Compose stack
make stop       # Stop all services
make test       # Run tests
make migrate    # Run migrations
make shell      # Open Tinker REPL
make bash       # Shell into container
make lint       # Code style fixes
```

## Conventions
- Follow Laravel conventions (Controllers, Models, Migrations)
- Use Eloquent ORM for database operations
- Routes in `routes/web.php` and `routes/api.php`
- Configuration via `.env` file
- Use Laravel validation for request data
- Use resource controllers for CRUD operations
